manifests.contents:
bench = []
example = []

[[bin]]
path = "src/main.rs"
name = "api_aga_in"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []

[[test]]
path = "tests/health_check.rs"
name = "health_check"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
edition = "2021"
required-features = []

[package]
name = "api_aga_in"
edition = "2021"
version = "0.0.1"
autobins = true
autoexamples = true
autotests = true
autobenches = true

[dependencies]
axum = "0.6.10"
config = "0.13.3"
hyper = "0.14.24"
tower = "0.4.13"
tower-request-id = "0.2.1"
tracing-bunyan-formatter = "0.3.6"
tracing-log = "0.1.3"

[dependencies.bonsaidb]
version = "0.4.1"
features = ["local", "local-async"]

[dependencies.serde]
version = "1.0.152"
features = ["derive"]

[dependencies.tokio]
version = "1.26.0"
features = ["full"]

[dependencies.tower-http]
version = "0.4.0"
features = ["trace"]

[dependencies.tracing]
version = "0.1.37"
features = ["log"]

[dependencies.tracing-subscriber]
version = "0.3.16"
features = ["registry", "env-filter"]

[dev-dependencies]
once_cell = "1.17.1"
reqwest = "0.11.14"
serial_test = "1.0.0"

[features]

[lib]
path = "src/lib.rs"
test = true
doctest = true
bench = true
doc = true
plugin = false
proc-macro = false
harness = true
required-features = []
